This paper is about automated machine learning (AutoML), which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on algorithm selection and hyperparameter tuning, which are important tasks in supervised learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since these sub-categories are closely related to machine learning. The paper also discusses matrix completion and active learning, which are topics in data science (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE), respectively.
